“The problem is not the tourists,” said Óscar Monge, head of the group representing the 195 owners of Binibeca Vell>. On the other hand, he pointed his finger at officials who, in his opinion, abandoned the residents with the noise generated by the constant parade of visitors and with the garbage > which accumulates daily.
