&nbsp; 
&nbsp;Il giudice ha vietato a Trump di attaccare verbalmente testimoni e giurati e gli ha comminato altri mille dollari di multa "per aver violato il suo ordine facendo commenti pubblici sulla giuria e su come è stata selezionata". Lo ha avvertito che future violazioni saranno "punibili con l'incarcerazione".

en_content:
AGI -&nbsp;The judge who presides over Donald Trump's historic criminal trial threatened to break down the former president if he doesn't stop talking in court. Trump continually violates the order of silence imposed by the judge. "Even if I don't want to impose a prison sanction, I want you to understand that I'm ready to do it," Judge Juan Merchan said.
&nbsp;
&nbsp; The judge forbade Trump to verbally attack witnesses and jurors and compeled him another thousand dollars of fine "for violating his order by making public comments on the jury and on how it was selected". He warned that future violations will be "punishable with incarceration".

